death. This is a great example of that. Graham was not the best senator but he was a reasonably decent Republican senator and he helped MAGA quite a bit, campaigning for Trump and voting with him.</p>\n<p>There is no good reason to be celebrating his death, but you fags are basically the same as people who celebrated Kirk\u2019s death: arrogant pompous clowns cheering for death because you saw a few TikTok videos and have determined the decedent is EVIL WAR MONGRUH / EVIL RACIST.</p>\n<p>I assure you, all of you have a far better chance of going to hell than Graham. Everyone who supported the Iraq War is not some evil Hitleresque supervillain. People can reasonably disagree on when and how we use our military. Supporting the war in Ukraine doesn\u2019t mean you deserve to die. You unhinged psychos may want to take some time and reflect on how you\u2019re the mirror image of a leftist demon before it\u2019s too late.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 58, "score_up": 68, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "BE\u00a0\u00a0LESS\u00a0\u00a0RETARDED", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2076081030495412371", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBqe4p9R", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 232, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8724245, "raw_content": "", "author": "PiratePatriotParrot", "created": 1783816489222, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "prisoner_of_funk", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBqe4p9R.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/WallStreetApes/status/2076081030495412371", "author_f